text: Circus Cowboy is a 1924 American western drama movie directed by William A. Wellman and starring Buck Jones, Marian Nixon, Jack McDonald, Ray Hallor, Marguerite Clayton. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox and is a lost movie. ==Other websites== * Category:1924 drama movies Category:1920s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:American drama movies Category:American silent movies Category:Movies directed by William A.
